                            <comment id="17313853" author="lirui" created="Fri, 2 Apr 2021 12:36:24 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Put more thoughts into this and I guess it&apos;s not a good idea to stop reading hive-site from classpath because that may break existing use cases. Instead, we can just prevent HiveConf from reading hive-site from the &lt;tt&gt;hiveSiteURL&lt;/tt&gt; variable.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
